  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Campaign</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Welcome to the unknown!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's 2058, the shuttle has endured heavy damage, has ran out of power and crashed into an unknown planet. Being stranded within the dark reaches of this so-called galaxy, what will you do? With the campaign, you can explore various planets as well as space stations to discover and learn about the mysteries surrounding this unfamiliar place.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757780/extras/47a990f4512a6e218f1d06f7b51b2cf2.poster.avif?t=1750036556\" width=628 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757780/extras/47a990f4512a6e218f1d06f7b51b2cf2.webm?t=1750036556\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757780/extras/47a990f4512a6e218f1d06f7b51b2cf2.mp4?t=1750036556\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Battle Mode</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Verse head to head against players as well as bots across various maps and gamemodes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757780/extras/c85fc31536a4df9374ea70c8b5d83ea9.poster.avif?t=1750036556\" width=628 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757780/extras/c85fc31536a4df9374ea70c8b5d83ea9.webm?t=1750036556\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757780/extras/c85fc31536a4df9374ea70c8b5d83ea9.mp4?t=1750036556\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Campaign</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Welcome to the unknown!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's 2058, the shuttle has endured heavy damage, has ran out of power and crashed into an unknown planet. Being stranded within the dark reaches of this so-called galaxy, what will you do? With the campaign, you can explore various planets as well as space stations to discover and learn about the mysteries surrounding this unfamiliar place.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757780/extras/47a990f4512a6e218f1d06f7b51b2cf2.poster.avif?t=1750036556\" width=628 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757780/extras/47a990f4512a6e218f1d06f7b51b2cf2.webm?t=1750036556\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757780/extras/47a990f4512a6e218f1d06f7b51b2cf2.mp4?t=1750036556\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Battle Mode</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Verse head to head against players as well as bots across various maps and gamemodes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757780/extras/c85fc31536a4df9374ea70c8b5d83ea9.poster.avif?t=1750036556\" width=628 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757780/extras/c85fc31536a4df9374ea70c8b5d83ea9.webm?t=1750036556\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757780/extras/c85fc31536a4df9374